Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  鷹志  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾遠一點  你這狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(167,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹志是哥哥  得護著小鳩一點才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跟那女人鬼混啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(253,323)\fs20}youji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹志很喜歡小鳩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要永遠和睦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我扯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波她沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波什麼都沒有做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這麼欺負波波啊
